high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove, then make a left and continue walking until you reach the white table with lettuce on it.
Pick up the fork on the table, between the knife and the spoon.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the sink.
Place the fork in the blue bowl, in the sink, turn the water on and wash the fork, turn the water off, and remove the fork.
Turn around and walk across the room to the end of the table with the bread on it.
Place the fork on the table, in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork on the white table, in front of the bread.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table with cabbage, bread and utensils.
Take the fork resting on top of the spatula.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink with running water and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the left side of the table.
Place the fork on the table in front of the bread on the right side of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Wash the fork in the sink and return it to the table.

high_descs: Walk until you're about a foot away from the stove then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the fork that's making a "T" on the spatula.
Turn left and walk to the sink that's in front of you to the right.
Clean the fork in the sink and then pick it back up and make sure to turn off the tap.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the wall in front of you and turn to the right when you get to it.
Put the fork under the bread horizontally.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the table.
